<topic id="topic_rm3_kkx_tn">
  <title>db.removeRG()</title>
  <body>
    <section>
      <title>NAME</title>
      <p>removeRG - Delete the database specified ReplicaGroup.</p>
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>SYNOPSIS</title>
      <p></p><apiname>db.removeRG</apiname>(<parmname>&lt;name></parmname>)
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>CATEGORY</title>
      <p></p>Sequoiadb
    </section>
    <section>
      <title>DESCRIPTION</title> 
      <p>Delete the database specified ReplicaGroup.</p>
      <parml>
        <plentry>
          <pt>name (string)</pt>
          <pd>ReplicaGroup name, the same database object, a unique ReplicaGroup name.
            <parml>
              <plentry>
                <pt>Format</pt>
                <pd>Definition Format removeRG() method, only the name field, name value is a string, required.</pd>
                <pd>(&lt;"ReplicaGroup name">)</pd>
              </plentry>
            </parml>
          </pd>          
        </plentry>        
      </parml>      
      <note>
        <ul><li>ReplicaGroup name must exist.</li>
        </ul></note>
    </section>    
    <section>
      <title>Examples</title>
      <p>Delete ReplicaGroup called "group" of.</p>
      <codeblock>db.removeRG("group")</codeblock>
    </section>
  </body>
